00:35:25,916 --> 00:35:26,833
He runs Sol?

690
00:35:26,916 --> 00:35:27,958
Yeah, he does.

691
00:35:28,041 --> 00:35:30,625
If we can demonstrate
a sustained flow of energy

692
00:35:30,708 --> 00:35:32,000
