he'll fund it and develop it.

695
00:35:36,333 --> 00:35:37,958
Sol Enterprises
is interested in...

696
00:35:38,041 --> 00:35:40,583
Yeah, he wants
to buy this patent.

697
00:35:40,666 --> 00:35:43,250
